● E9002: Internal crate version override [Rust Interop]
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  ⓘ Cannot override internal crate "tokio" (v1)

  💡 Liva uses tokio v1 internally. The crate is already available inside rust { } blocks. To add features: use rust "tokio" features ["..."]

  📚 Learn more: https://github.com/liva-lang/livac/blob/main/docs/ERROR_CODES.md#e9002
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
